name: MyLove
0:
”Alexa, open My Love”
”Alexa, start My Love”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my love
des:
Say, "Alexa, open My Love" any time of day or night to hear something that inspires, strengthens, or gives you something good to think about.

When using My Love, you can say "Alexa, next" to receive another. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
